Zhihong Zhai

Welcome to the Centipede Game!
             Have fun!!!


           3 lives each game
Arrow keys for Hero's movement
# keys for switching weapon
                 F to fire
         U to increase difficulty
         D to decrease difficulty
          P to pause & resume


Mushroom                      +30 pts
Centipede                      +100 pts
Contact Centipede           -200 pts
Monster                        +300 pts
Contact Monster             -300 pts
Monster eats Mushroom    -50 pts



          Weapon Features:
lvl 1: 1 bullet each time
lvl 2: bullets ignore mushrooms
lvl 3: 2 bullets each time
lvl 4: bullets detroy objects in the
same column (no pts for mushrooms)       